00:31:18.696 --> 00:31:22.296
Can you comment on any differences in terms of biology of the

516
00:31:22.356 --> 00:31:24.856
disease and ctDNA dynamics?

517
00:31:26.516 --> 00:31:29.756
So we don't have all of the data broken down yet by

