00:32:07.816 --> 00:32:11.376
Ranjan Upadhyay. He's presenting a Phase

532
00:32:11.576 --> 00:32:15.256
2 study of adjuvant PD-1 blockade with endocrine

533
00:32:15.336 --> 00:32:18.716
therapy in hormone receptor-positive and inflammatory breast cancer:

534
00:32:19.296 --> 00:32:22.756
circulating biomarkers and molecular correlates of clinical outcomes.

535
00:32:28.676 --> 00:32:32.516
Thank you, Dr. Kopetz, for the introduction, and thank you to the

