621
00:37:44.884 --> 00:37:47.704
risk and response to checkpoint blockade.

622
00:37:50.644 --> 00:37:54.504
We did do some clonal analysis to see the evolution of these tumor

623
00:37:54.564 --> 00:37:57.364
clones from the primary tumor site to the lymph node.

624
00:37:57.904 --> 00:38:01.784
Now, this is a very small N, and we didn't find any consistent patterns

625
00:38:01.844 --> 00:38:03.504
