689
00:41:49.184 --> 00:41:49.664
over

690
00:41:50.664 --> 00:41:51.844
prior historical data.

691
00:41:52.844 --> 00:41:56.664
We found patterns of copy number variation between the primary metastatic

692
00:41:56.744 --> 00:41:59.384
