697
00:42:15.004 --> 00:42:18.544
months and correlated with shorter disease-free survival,

698
00:42:20.244 --> 00:42:23.824
and ctDNA negativity at the end of treatment was associated with

699
00:42:23.844 --> 00:42:27.324
100% disease-free survival at 24 months, which is

700
00:42:27.364 --> 00:42:30.744
remarkable for a disease entity like IBC.

701
00:42:32.384 --> 00:42:36.084
So with that, I'd like to thank Bora Lim, who led the study,

702
00:42:36.544 --> 00:42:40.424
the MD Anderson IBC team who

