00:53:28.780 --> 00:53:32.380
interception because there was no radiological or clinical progression.

886
00:53:33.420 --> 00:53:37.060
The patient received five out of the six planned doses of

887
00:53:37.080 --> 00:53:40.920
plerixafor and the reason why this was stopped earlier it was

