00:53:45.140 --> 00:53:47.580
leading to the patient to ask for discontinuation of the drug.

890
00:53:48.540 --> 00:53:52.400
However, as you can see in this slide, there is a very nice clearance of

891
00:53:52.440 --> 00:53:55.580
the ctDNA shortly after starting plerixafor,

892
00:53:56.280 --> 00:54:00.180
clearance that persist 12 months after discontinuation of the plerixafor,

